8 An Act relating to the Bringing Sitcoms Home from
Hollywood Pilot Program Revolving Fund; making an
9 appropriation; specifying amount, source, and
purpose; and providing for noncodification.
10
11
12
13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
15 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
16 There is hereby appropriated to the Bringing Sitcoms Home from
17 Hollywood Pilot Program Revolving Fund created pursuant to Section
18 3642.6 of Title 68 of the Oklahoma Statutes from any monies not
19 otherwise appropriated from the Filmed in Oklahoma Program Revolving
20 Fund created pursuant to Section 3639 of Title 68 of the Oklahoma
21 Statutes, the sum of Five Million Dollars ($5,000,000.00) to be
22 budgeted and expended in accordance with law.
